<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Title</title>
    <script type="text/javascript">
        function mychange() {
            var x = document.getElementById('frame');
            x.value = x.value.toUpperCase();
        }
    </script>

</head>
<body>
请输入英文字符<input type="text" id="frame" onchange="mychange()">
<p>当您离开输入字段时，会触发将输入文本转换为大写的函数。</p>


</body>
</html>